#AQUAMARINE#"How convenient...  so much Sher'Tul magic for my taking...  magic to turn against its creators...  but now... one new obstacle...  one last great warrior under the waves..."#WHITE#]], [[As the %s falls dead, bubbles start forming beneath you, then frothing as the water grows uncomfortably warm.
#AQUAMARINE#"Thank you...  interloper..."#WHITE# a low voice rumbles.
